                            <comment id="13500851" author="ralph.goers@dslextreme.com" created="Tue, 20 Nov 2012 06:00:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This was a mistake. The concatenated name is used by the QueueManager to insure only a single manager will exist for the queue. The name should be configured on the appender.  This has been fixed in revision 1411553. Please verify and close.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13502280" author="bekisz" created="Wed, 21 Nov 2012 20:25:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Works perfectly. Thanks ! &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
